.TH k2i-completions-fish 1  "k2i-completions-fish "
.SH NAME
k2i\-completions\-fish \- Generate fish completions
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBk2i\-completions\-fish\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate fish completions
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.SH EXTRA
EXAMPLE:
  k2i completions fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/k2i.fish
